Java Font Editor
Preference > Editor > ColorScheme > ColorSchemeFont >   (CodeBar)
Preference > Editor > ColorScheme > ConsoleFont >       (Console)
Preference > Appearance & Behavior > Appearance > size  (SideBar)

Java Run Code keys setting:
Preference > KeyMap > MainMenu > Run > Run > AddKeyBoardShortCut(Insert Want's Keys) > Apply > Ok



